  </section>

  <!-- Service Types -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 text-center">
        Types of Online Mental Health Care
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-10 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Understanding your options helps you choose the right service.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">
              üí¨
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900">Online Therapy</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Traditional talk therapy via messaging, video, or phone with licensed therapists (LCSW, LPC, LMFT).
            Best for anxiety, depression, stress, relationships, and general mental wellness.
          </p>
          <div class="text-sm">
            <div class="font-medium text-slate-900 mb-2">Best Platforms:</div>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-slate-600">
              <li>‚Ä¢ BetterHelp: Largest network</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Talkspace: Insurance accepted</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ $65-110/week average</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">
              üíä
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900">Psychiatric Care</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Medication management with licensed psychiatrists or psychiatric nurse practitioners. Best for
            moderate to severe depression, anxiety, ADHD, and conditions requiring medication.
          </p>
          <div class="text-sm">
            <div class="font-medium text-slate-900 mb-2">Best Platforms:</div>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-slate-600">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Cerebral: Therapy + meds</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Brightside: Psychiatry-focused</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ $85-325/month average</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">
              üéØ
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900">Specialized Therapy</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Targeted treatment for specific issues like couples counseling, trauma (EMDR/CBT), addiction,
            grief, or career coaching with specialized practitioners.
          </p>
          <div class="text-sm">
            <div class="font-medium text-slate-900 mb-2">Common Specialties:</div>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-slate-600">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Cognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT)</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Couples & relationship counseling</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Trauma & PTSD treatment</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-600 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">
              üì±
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900">Self-Guided Tools</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Apps and digital therapeutics offering meditation, mood tracking, CBT exercises, and wellness content.
            Good for mild symptoms or as supplement to therapy.
          </p>
          <div class="text-sm">
            <div class="font-medium text-slate-900 mb-2">Popular Options:</div>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-slate-600">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Headspace: Meditation</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Calm: Sleep & anxiety</li>
