      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section id="how-it-works" class="section-light">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 text-center">How Online Therapy Works</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-accent/10 text-brand-accent flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 font-bold text-xl">
            1
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">Take Assessment</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
            Complete a brief questionnaire about your mental health needs and preferences.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-accent/10 text-brand-accent flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 font-bold text-xl">
            2
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">Get Matched</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
            Algorithm matches you with a licensed therapist who fits your needs within 24-48 hours.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-accent/10 text-brand-accent flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 font-bold text-xl">
            3
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">Start Therapy</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
            Communicate via messaging, video, phone, or live chat based on your preference.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-accent/10 text-brand-accent flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 font-bold text-xl">
            4
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">Ongoing Support</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
            Regular sessions, unlimited messaging (most platforms), and ability to switch therapists anytime.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 text-center">
        Common Questions
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="group card p-6">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-semibold cursor-pointer list-none text-slate-900">
            <span>Is online therapy as effective as in-person?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-brand-accent">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
            Research shows online therapy (teletherapy) is equally effective as traditional in-person therapy for
            most conditions including anxiety, depression, and stress. The key is finding a licensed therapist you
            connect with, regardless of format. Some people actually prefer the convenience and comfort of online sessions.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group card p-6">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-semibold cursor-pointer list-none text-slate-900">
            <span>How much does online therapy cost?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-brand-accent">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
            Most platforms charge $65-110 per week ($260-440/month) for unlimited messaging plus weekly live sessions.
            This is typically cheaper than traditional therapy which averages $100-200 per session. Some platforms
            like Talkspace accept insurance which can significantly reduce costs.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group card p-6">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-semibold cursor-pointer list-none text-slate-900">
            <span>Are online therapists real licensed professionals?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-brand-accent">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
            Yes. Reputable platforms like BetterHelp, Talkspace, and others only work with licensed, credentialed
            therapists (LCSW, LPC, LMFT, psychologists) who are licensed in your state. They undergo background
            checks and credential verification. Always verify your therapist's credentials in your first session.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group card p-6">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-semibold cursor-pointer list-none text-slate-900">
            <span>What if I don't like my therapist?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-brand-accent">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
            Most platforms make it easy to switch therapists anytime at no extra cost. Finding the right therapeutic
            fit is crucial for effective treatment, so don't hesitate to request a new match if you don't feel
            comfortable or aren't making progress with your current therapist.
          </p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Related Content -->
  <section class="section-light border-t border-slate-200">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 text-center">
        Explore More Categories
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
